:::card{title="2 · Technical Documentation"}
A CLI reference page: API surface, architecture diagram, code blocks,
warnings, examples, tabs, cross-links — all from one `.noma` file.

[Open rendered artifact →](./examples/tech-doc.html)
[Source](https://github.com/ferax564/noma/blob/main/examples/tech-doc.noma) · [LLM](./examples/tech-doc.llm.txt) · [JSON](./examples/tech-doc.json)
